{"word":"τορέω","slug":"τορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τορέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>τόρος</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to bore through, pierce</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to proclaim in shrill piercing tones</i>, in <a href='S:reduplication'>redupl.</a> <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>τετορήσω</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>τορός.</el><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>τορνεύω</el>, <i>to work, shape</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}